FLOW OF A TRIAL

Wait for fixation
Allow fixation to stabilize: 0.05s
Hold fixation: Minimum 0.5s + draw from exponential with mean 0.3s (max 1.6s tot)
RDM: Minimum 0.35s + draw from exponential with mean 0.2s (max 1s total)
Wait: 0.33s
Decision: 2s max
Allow saccade to stabilize: 0.05s
Hold at target: 0.2s
Reward solenoid open time: 0.1s + (steps of 0.04s for consecutive corrects - max 0.3s)

Timeout for wrong choice: 4s
Intertrial interval: 2s




